## ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

## NOTE: The DFA-based scanner only implements:
##   1. Integers, 2. Floats, 3. Identifiers, 4. Booleans
##   5. Operators, 6. Punctuators, 7. Comments
##
## Strings and characters are NOT in the DFA specification,
## so they will be tokenized as individual characters/errors.

